channel.title: Host not able to login
channel.description: So, my computer wasn't able to host anymore for some reason. So, I got a new host and setup everything on his computer. Everything works, people can get on. The only problem is that the host can't get on. He has two computers, and can't get on the server with any of them. I even tried making him login with localhost. Nothing will work for him. So, my computer wasn’t able to host anymore for some reason. So, I got a new host and setup everything on his computer. Everything works, people can get on. The only problem is that the host can’t get on. He has two computers, and can’t get on the server with any of them. I even tried making him login with localhost. Nothing will work for him.
